{"tid":1154441,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"PRODUCE 101 JAPAN 討論區","createTime":"2019-05-14T10:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T12:41:03.000Z","uid":251649,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a25d17e3b6d2d87e2b2719b6c88bf60379e7e700","tid":1154441,"uid":251649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:01:23.000Z","msg":"日本初！由國民製作人決定的男子團體選秀開催<br />\nPRODUCE系列由韓國公司Mnet開始推出，而PRODUCE 101 JAPAN就係日本版<br />\n<br />\n國民製作人代表係吉本興業嘅岡村隆史同矢部浩之<br />\n<br />\n16歲以上至30歲以下，素人都參加得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但</span></span>唔可以有所屬公司<br />\n報名截止於5月31日<br />\n<br />\n2019春天播放<br />\n官網：<a href=\"https://produce101.jp/#top-about\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fproduce101.jp%2F%23top-about&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=2ba01c32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://produce101.jp/#top-about</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人嘅話我再考慮po啲已報名嘅人俾大家睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce520b79fb3a5c04b22031760f3bfc3e7ce19f7","tid":1154441,"uid":251649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:45:01.000Z","msg":"好慘，邊度都冇熱度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad4129b32158ed5b11a8ea3da5f0ec68107c894","tid":1154441,"uid":251649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60aebb845bd68bd33ff0324eec9e35ab4eb1961a","tid":1154441,"uid":238483,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:45:28.000Z","msg":"依家播緊produce x101仲邊有人睇日本版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1943b4a7fd862df5218b927d4bfe5938e513a899","tid":1154441,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:23:45.000Z","msg":"分組時應該聽到好多j家既歌<br />\n又易唱 d舞又hea<img src=\"/assets/fa